      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Practical, affordable, and ready for its next owner, this vehicle is a solid opportunity for anyone seeking dependable basic transportation at a budget-friendly price. It shows its age, but it offers strong value for the money and would make a sensible choice for a commuter, first-time buyer, or project-minded shopper. Priced to attract attention and backed by straightforward representation, this is an economical way to get on the road without overspending.",
