      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little runabout that\u2019s far from perfect, but it still has plenty to offer the right buyer. If you\u2019re after a cheap, usable car for a project, spare vehicle, or simple A-to-B motoring, this one could be a great fit. It shows its age and needs a bit of TLC, which is reflected in the price, but it\u2019s a straightforward car being sold by someone who\u2019d rather be upfront than dress it up. A great opportunity for someone handy or anyone wanting affordable wheels without spending a fortune.",
